'''Orbi Dubai''' is an interactive visitor attraction in [[Dubai]], [[United Arab Emirates]], which opened on 7th May 2017. Created by Japanese technology firm [[SEGA]] in collaboration with [[BBC Worldwide]] and Dubai shopping mall operator Majid Al Futtaim, this is the third [[Orbi]] attraction in the world and the first to open outside of [[Japan]].
