''The Bunker'' is a comic book written by [[Joshua Hale Fialkov]] with artwork by [[Joe Infurnari]].
A pilot television episode was announced to have been written for Lionsgate TV.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/11/05/joshua-hale-fialkov-adapting-the-bunker-for-lionsgate-tv/|title=Joshua Hale Fialkov Adapting The Bunker For Lionsgate TV|author=Brendon Connelly|work=Bleeding Cool Comic Book, Movie, TV News}}</ref>
==Plot== The world population is dying, and those responsible send a bunker back in time to warn their younger selves, in order to prevent it.
==Reception== It was highly recommended by [[Ain't It Cool News]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/63600#7|title=AICN COMICS REVIEWS: JMS’ SIDEKICK! Fialkov’s THE BUNKER! Lemire’s TRILLIUM! WEIRD TALES ! & MORE!|author=ambush bug|date=7 August 2013|work=Aint It Cool News}}</ref> [[Newsarama]] gave it a 9 out of 10.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsarama.com/20319-best-shots-rapid-reviews-she-hulk-1-jla-12-nearly-20-others.html|title=Best Shots Rapid Reviews: SHE-HULK #1, JLA #12, Nearly 20 Others!|work=Newsarama.com}}</ref> [[Bleeding Cool]] called it “A beautiful comic.”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/11/05/joshua-hale-fialkov-adapting-the-bunker-for-lionsgate-tv/|title=Joshua Hale Fialkov Adapting The Bunker For Lionsgate TV - Bleeding Cool News And Rumors|date=5 November 2013|publisher=}}</ref> [[Comic Vine]] gave it 5 stars.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://comicvine.gamespot.com/reviews/the-bunker-1/1900-2711/|title=The Bunker #1 Review|publisher=}}</ref> [[Kotaku]] called it "a great, tense read with a killer twist ending that will have you aching for more."<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/what-happens-when-you-find-out-your-older-self-kills-th-1070987344|title=What Happens When You Find Out Your Older Self Kills the World|author=Evan Narcisse|publisher=Gawker Media|work=Kotaku}}</ref>
